BLAST - Class in mage.Tools
BLAST or Basic Local Search Alignment Tool, developed by Myers, Altschul, Gish, Miller and Lipman is an algorithm for comparing primary biological sequence information, such as the amino-acid sequences of different proteins or the nucleotides of DNA sequences.
